  "conclusion": "The c8 fullnative bug is not at layer3 full-attention input and not an immediate large layer3 output failure. The first over-atol effect appears when layer4 computes linear-attention attn_input from the slightly-drifted layer3 output, then amplifies by layer7 pre-QKV. Candidate fix targets are layer3 full-attention output numerical parity, layer4 RMSNorm sensitivity/precision, or a need to keep rowchunk/per-row semantics through the layer3\u21924 handoff.",
  "created_at": "2026-06-07T06:31:50.977294+00:00",
