    "layer4_input": "after layer3 handoff / layer4 RMSNorm, fullnative layer4 attn_input has first over-atol drift (max_abs 0.0078125 row0) while rowchunk remains exact.",
    "layer4_output": "drift collapses back to under-atol by layer4 output in the L8/decode1 window, explaining why short final output can remain eq_ok.",
    "layer7_preqkv": "fullnative over-atol drift expands to all rows by layer7 pre-QKV; rowchunk remains exact."
